===Noun===
'''dilemma''' (''plural:'' '''dilemmata''' ''or'' '''dilemmas''')

# A [[circumstance]] in which a choice must be made between two alternatives that seem equally undesirable.
# (''disputed'') A difficult circumstance or [[problem]].

====Usage notes====
*The original meaning of this term is a choice between two alternatives only, by [[dint]] of its etymology.  While some speakers and writers use the term as a synonym for "problem", this usage is considered non-standard, and is avoided by careful users.

